Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:05.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(432,508)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来份怪物蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Monster Krabby Patty, please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,356)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好久没人点怪物蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's ordered a Monster Patty in ages
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.59,0:01:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份怪物蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Monster Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.03,0:01:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是说了怪物蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,D-d-did you say a M-Monster Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.78,0:01:20.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份怪物蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:20.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Monster Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.37,0:01:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪物蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Monster Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.42,0:01:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能成的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数到三  就翻面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At the count of three, we flip
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.69,0:01:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.72,0:01:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.80,0:01:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.01,0:01:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.91,0:01:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spat?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.92,0:02:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好还是继续工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we'd better get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.67,0:02:30.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:30.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还怎么继续工作  明明都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could I go back to work without
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明明没了铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without Spat?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换个别的锅铲用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Use another spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能用的只有一把锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is only one spatula for me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that is Spat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spat, wait up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了  铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, Spat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,428)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在一起经历了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been through so much together
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这真的很难说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no easy way to say this
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  如果我是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, if I were you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.45,0:03:55.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会认真开始考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would give serious consideration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to start thinking about
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换把新锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a replacement spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去吧  休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go home, get some rest
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.21,0:04:03.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:03.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽己所能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,try to do everything we can
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢医生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not a doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是个在找合适角色的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm an actor researching for a role
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.20,0:04:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快领到这段的戏份了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so totally gonna get this part
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换把新锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Replacement spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有东西能换
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could anything ever replace
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1068,820)}阿铲在内
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来好高贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So shiny
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这线条  好有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those lines, so
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sleek
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在说什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用不着这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.57,0:04:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能确实需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I do need this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就会认真考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would give serious consideration to
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换把新锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a replacement spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准摸阿铲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No touchy-touchy the Le Spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.84,0:05:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿铲特别特别的贵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's very, very expensive
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然  如果你买下这个上品物件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you purchase this fine item
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you may
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿着它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我口袋里有一点零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got some loose change in my pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些够付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will this cover it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.11,0:05:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.38,0:05:31.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:31.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630,940)}裤头村房产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,372)}售出
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有家当就这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's everything I have
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在可以买阿铲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now can I buy Le Spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有家当是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣服不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice outfit
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傍晩好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶好  你最近如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Granny, what's shakin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天有点风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breezy today
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣服不错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice outfit, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱花得很值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was worth every penny
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛在浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all the lollygagging about?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.88,0:06:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  快去看海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, get a load of SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好是什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This better be good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家马上就会知晓你的美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon everyone will know of your beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(548,816)}阿铲
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  里面是怎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, what's going on in
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你难道连一点羞耻心都没有吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any shame, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的羞耻心都到这里面去了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:32.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All my shame went in here, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,754)}阿铲
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿铲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Le Spa-tu-ler
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in blazes isthat?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以解决我工作的一点小难题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just the answer to our little production dilemma
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这玩意能干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what can it do?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让我变出名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it make me famous?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不仅应有尽有  还不止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything you want and more
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好刺激的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me have a go at it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.86,0:06:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no can do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是要跟你老板唱反调吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you going against your commanding officer?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.99,0:07:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是超级高科技产品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is a highly developed piece of engineering
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想掌握它得慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that takes quality time to master
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你有了这个花哨机器  那你最好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With that fancy machinery, I expect you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让做蟹黄堡的速度给我翻倍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make Krabby Patties twice as fast
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这应该不成问题  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think that'll be a problem, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿铲3000为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Le Spatula 3000, at your service
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要看它能不能再让我大开眼界一回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see that thing impress me even more--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我招呼更多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by bringing in more customers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往我腰包多塞一点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and more money in me pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿铲的能力一定会让你难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You won't believe what Le Spatula is capable of
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好大显神威没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready to show 'em, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  没必要这么害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, no need to be shy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班第一天都比较难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's always tough the first day on the job
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能来一份蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get one Krabby Patty, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  来一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I need one Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡  马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty coming up lickety-split
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗  阿铲兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spat, is there something wrong, pal?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我碰不得垃圾食物  就比如这种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would not dare touch such slop as this
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么说来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how you say
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.89,0:07:59.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我生来就是制作顶级菜肴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am designed for the utmost in culinary cuisine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,岂有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No less
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.07,0:08:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们应该是朋友的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I thought we were friends
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.11,0:08:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们甚至都不在同一个社会阶层里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are not even in the same social class
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.99,0:08:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,享受你平庸的一生吧  煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a nice life of mediocrity, fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿铲  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Le Spatula, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为你放弃了所有家当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gave up everything for you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还是有感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had something
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这算哪门子感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's that for something?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  俗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Au revoir, peasant
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你在这家小破餐馆打工愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun ladling in your greasy spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿铲走了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My spatula's gone, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你没了锅铲要怎么做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how are you gonna flip Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without a spatu-ler?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从前有一把锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hada spatula once
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一把真正的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a real spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与我同甘共苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one that stood by me through thick and thin
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与我面对油骨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through grease and gristle
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而我却背叛了他的忠实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I betrayed his loyalty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就像傻子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like a fool
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是有点喜欢你的旧锅铲的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always did like your old spatu-ler
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.36,0:08:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它每次都能把工作做好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He got the job done right every time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.05,0:09:06.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要以锅铲的行为来评判锅铲的好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:06.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The truemeasure of a good spatula is by his actions
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.03,0:09:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能以什么花哨铬合金跟按钮来评判
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not by some fancy chrome and buttons
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须回去找我的旧锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to find my old spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go to him
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go now, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁着我客人还没跑光赶紧去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go before I lose all me customers
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It can't be true
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太晩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很遗憾要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell you this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.03,0:09:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在已经到了天国的厨房抽屉里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's moved on to that big kitchen drawer in the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逝去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我想说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有领到戏份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't get the acting part
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  这个不是你的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the way, that's not your spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你兄弟已经在医院里被修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your buddy's all patched up in the infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,272)}医院
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好高兴你康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:58.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're better
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不是要故意背叛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I didn't mean to betray you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板需要替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs needed a replacement
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟蟹黄堡肉饼不会自己翻自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties don't flip themselves, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那只是一时糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a moment of weakness
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.69,0:10:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪光的未必是金子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All that glitters is not gold
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:48.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,382)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.76,0:11:02.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也找不到像他一样的锅铲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:02.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never find another spatula like him again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.79,0:11:08.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:08.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲铲  既然我们又团圆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spatula, now that we're together again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何一切都不会把我们分开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing will ever separate us
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份怪物蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Monster Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  我们能成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, buddy, we can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.48,0:11:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.80,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,0)}许愿井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.26\pos(238,456)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:49.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.26\pos(486,722)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.26\pos(384,398)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.26\pos(508,660)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.26\pos(430,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥都没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来好像有两毛五在大声呼救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a quarter crying for help
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.89,0:12:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到爸爸这来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to papa
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站在这别动  这位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这两毛五是我儿子刚掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My son just dropped that quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得那小孩看起来鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that kid looks pretty shifty to me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怕不会是偷的这两毛五吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do I know he didn't steal it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个小屁孩把好端端的钱给丢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That little brat's throwing perfectly good money away
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果我弄不到钱  谁都不准
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if I can't have it, no one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望他把你所有退休金都扔洞里去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope he throws all your retirement money down a hole
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的两毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor little quarter
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.99,0:12:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座井里全是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This well is full of money
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.33,0:12:36.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:36.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, little fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会救你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我屁股太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me poop deck's too big
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许个愿吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make a wish, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.68,0:12:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有愿望都已经实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All my wishes have already come true
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会来救你的  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you, money
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.49,0:13:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些没心没肺的畜生是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you heartless brutes think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用许愿井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Using the wishing well
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把硬币丢进去再许个愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you toss in a coin and make a wish
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.97,0:13:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没别的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing else happens
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's fun
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是说会有傻子把钱扔洞里玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean suckers throw money down a hole for fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直就是天大的骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the greatest scam ever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能把两毛五还回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we have our quarter back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428,452)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  蟹黄堡怎么还没做好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, why aren't those patties ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美不是催出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't rush perfection
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我催的不是完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not rushing perfection
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,催的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm rushing you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总是好会开玩笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always the kidder, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这工作烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This job stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过至少我还没去挖什么水沟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But at least I'm not digging ditches
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.47,0:13:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有新工作要给你们做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a new job for you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,X是标记点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,X marks the spot
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,标记了尤金蟹纪念许愿井的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the Eugene Krabs memorial wishing well
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边要挖许愿井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wishing well, here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是必须先死了才能做纪念的玩意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to be dead to have a memorial anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  难道你不相信魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, don't you believe in magic?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你难道不相信魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't you believe in magic?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板一样也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And neither does Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我反正相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I do
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.21,0:14:00.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座井会让好多梦想成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:00.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This well's gonna make a lot of dreams come true
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要先许个什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the first thing you're gonna wish for?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟你离得越远越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To be as far away from you as possible
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这破洞可不会自己挖自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob, this hole's not gonna dig itself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肯定也不去挖这个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm certainly not gonna do it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你激不激动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, aren't you excited?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这井肯定会帮上好多人的忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is really gonna help people
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿上硬币还有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a penny and some magic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪怕生活悲惨无比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even though your life is tragic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都能把梦想丢进井里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can throw all your dreams down the well
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪怕每天痛苦难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Although every day, the pain grows
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,彩虹之上骑独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll ride unicorns on rainbows
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.98,0:14:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把梦想丢进井里就能成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you throw all your dreams down the well
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(503.7,288)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每当你的生活即将崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When your life's come apart at the seams
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你放弃你的所有梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you've given up all your dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了这些方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here is just the means
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能让梦想实现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To make those dreams come true
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不再受苦  不再叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more sufferin', no more sighin'
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不再疼痛  不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more pain and no more cryin'
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把梦想丢进井里就能成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you throw all your dreams down the well
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:49.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752,766)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Squidward, what do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那是我听过最难听的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the worst song I ever heard
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过至少这口破井挖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But at least this stupid well's finished
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们闻到了吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You smell that, boys?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是钱的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the smell of money
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想说的是不是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean magic, don't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能闻到的就只有那个垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I can smell is that Dumpster
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你可以回去收银了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Squidward, you can go back to the register
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要没歌就成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as there's no singing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.24,0:15:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟蟹黄堡还有一场约会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've got a date with a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别走  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先带你看看你的全新工作场所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you your new station
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算是升职吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kind of a promotion
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,升一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sort of
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有升职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A promotion?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为什么要下到井里去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go down in the well?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要让你来收钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To collect the money
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得待在这下面多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long do I have to stay down here?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,八小时后见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you in eight hours
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢让我升职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the promotion
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里真的好黑好吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure is dark and scary in here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好希望能有个高档望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure wish I had a fancy telescope
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能在海底用的望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One that works underwater
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就可以让我高兴得不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'd make me happier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a june bug at a porch light sale
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our very first wish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及下一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait till it comes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.30,0:15:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经依照传统给你了一笔小钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have presented you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a monetary offering, as custom dictates
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的愿望  又名命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wish, nay, my command
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是变高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is to be taller
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a little
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大到可以粉碎我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just big enough to crush my enemies
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消灭那些虫豸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like the vermin they are
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我希望能有辆漂亮新船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a snazzy new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想当个赛船辣妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be a hotrod mama
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:19.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这是座许愿井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, this is a wishing well
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿个硬币投进去许个愿就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just throw in a coin and make a wish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  会说话的神奇垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, magical talking trashcan
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我希望海绵宝宝能在这看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish SpongeBob were here to see this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.53,0:16:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got my wish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你投币应该得先放手才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're supposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let go of the coin when you throw it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I got my wish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我下班还有六个半小时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we got six and a half hours till the end of my shift
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在想干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:47.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.92,0:16:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag, you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你收获如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what kind of haul did you get?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不错了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did great, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了珊迪的半毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a nickel from Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师的两分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two pennies from Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板的一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a penny from Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有副九成新的假牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this slightly used pair of dentures
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我头朝下掉了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I fell on my head
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星或许可以卖掉几个钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can probably get a couple of bucks for Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最好把钱都交过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better just send up the money
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.53,0:17:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,修这许愿井的想法可真不错  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This wishing well was a wonderful idea, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家的愿望都成真了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Has anyone's wish come true yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not yet
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我确定如果你有坚实的信心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure, if you believe strong enough
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挖得够深的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and dug deep enough
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家的愿望就都会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everyone's wishes will come true
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的没错  随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure, whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在能出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we come out now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodness, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须要待在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta stay down there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以备大半夜有人来这许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just in case any late-night wishers come by
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等天亮了我再来找你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be back for you at dawn
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家的愿望都没实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's wishes are coming true
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们哪里做错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did we do wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道我有坚实的信心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know I believe hard enough
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是我挖得不够深
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I just didn't dig deep enough
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说怎么样  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好要挖魔法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to dig for some magic?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法已经消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, the magic has gone missin'
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家仍然还在许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And everyone's still wishin'
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而他们的梦想都已然落空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But their dreams have fallen flat upon the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法就藏在石头下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll find magic under rubble
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  铲子快拿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Patrick, grab a shovel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.38,0:18:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法在这里就可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here is where the magic can be found
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们身处井底之下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're at the bottom of a well
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样不是很好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, man, won't it be swell
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.69,0:18:19.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我们让大家愿望都实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:19.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When we make everyone's wishes all come true?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy mackerel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔法被我们碰见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've struck magic
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that good?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我除了当厨师之外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next to being a fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所做的最重大的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's the most important thing I've ever done
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我唯一做过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing I've ever done
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这底下开不开心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Having fun down there, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星居然也在这底下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's down there, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这好事真是越来越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It just gets better and better
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要许个愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to make a wish?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿望已经实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got my wish
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个被困在了个黑暗的洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two are stuck in a dark hole
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还离我远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们找到魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found the magic
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没有魔法  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no magic, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.31,0:19:01.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许愿井是专门用来骗你们这种傻子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:01.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishing wells are just a scam to fool saps like you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们真的找到魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did find the magic
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你能亲眼看见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish you could see it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.73,0:19:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你想好要来参加派对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you decided to join the party
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Party
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们才刚要玩点派对游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were just gonna play some party games
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到了  你当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tag, you're it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没办法爬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no way to climb outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你上臂力气再大一点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you had more upper-arm strength
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  你应该要多多锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you should work out more
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如我现在就开始锻炼得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't I just start right now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.41,0:19:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟我现在在这就有俩傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, I got a couple of dumbbells right here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:40.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1054.464,920)}哑 铃
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能别靠得这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you not stand so close?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要害我得幽闭恐惧症了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making me claustrophobic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(449.624,920)}圣诞老人
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幽闭恐惧症是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does claustrophobic mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是他怕圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means he's afraid of Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.14,0:19:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.81,0:19:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会吓到人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're scaring him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样没用的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not working, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.30,0:19:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你踩到我脚上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, You're standing on my foot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.90,0:20:01.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:01.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肘子碰到我排骨上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you got your elbow in my ribs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也别踩我的土豆沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And stop stepping in my potato salad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别推我了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop pushing me, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, like this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不应该在这里打架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't fight in here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.42,0:20:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是有魔法的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a magical place
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  从我身上下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, get off of me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过我有幽闭恐惧症
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you I am claustrophobic
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜这里没有圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but there's no Santa Claus here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看你收获如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what you got
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, it's heavy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定有好多的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be a lot of money
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm free
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这下面干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What were you doing down there?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可绝对不批加班费
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't approve any overtime
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.37,0:20:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道你是黑灯瞎火偷偷来这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or were you sneaking here, in the dead of night
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许霸王愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for free wishes?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.94,0:20:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我唯一许的愿就是能离这远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing I wish for is to be far away from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,664)}特别特别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,664)}远远的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.17,0:21:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your trip
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lucky
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你昨晩赚到了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So how much money did you make last night?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们没赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We didn't get any money
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们找到了更好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we found something better
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们找到魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found the magic
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在井里往深了挖  找到了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We dug down deeper in the well and found the magic
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有的愿望都要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all the wishes will come true
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen closely, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现实中想要的东西不是许愿许出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't get what you want in life just by wishing for it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是个什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the deep blue is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晩会有满月出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a full moon out tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们喜欢我许愿要的望远镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you like my new telescope I wished for?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不错  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许愿井真的好有用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That wishing well sure does work
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.39,0:21:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧合而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a coincidence
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得我的新赛船如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my new hotrod?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是漂亮  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不让我开一下兜兜风看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's about letting me take it for a spin?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.30,0:21:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准兜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她那艘船是许愿许来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She wished for that boat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思就是那船是偷来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean she stole that boat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  海绵宝宝蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, SpongeBob, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beautiful day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.59,0:22:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你总能相信了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that proof enough for you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想骗我相信魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never get me to believe in magic
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.99,0:22:13.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:13.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.80,0:22:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,证明给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just to prove it to you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.26,0:22:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,示范一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll demonstrate
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.84,0:22:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我希望我被人清蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I was steamed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.44,0:22:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配以融化的黄油而食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and served with a side of melted butter
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.55,0:22:24.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:24.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.56,0:22:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的魔法在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, where's your magic now?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.26,0:22:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这是在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:41.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(906,340)}完
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.02,0:22:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我相信魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do believe in magic
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.85,0:22:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
